description: A close result is expected in next month's poll, but campaigns will develop their own momentum.
title: Irish general election: What's at stake for the parties?
title_page: Irish general election: What's at stake for the parties? - BBC News
maintext: The UK will leave the EU during the course of the campaign on 31 January and Fine Gael hopes it will get a boost from voters being reminded by what they see as its sure-footed handling of the issue.
